features: Sheet Mask with Skin-Loving Ingredients: This soothing sheet mask is made with a biodegradable base and enriched with naturally nourishing actives, making it ideal for all skin types—including sensitive skin.

Instant Hydration & Long-Lasting Calm: Powered by PAPAYALURONIC, this formula combines papaya extract and 8 hyaluronic acids to hydrate all five layers of the skin while soothing the skin for a calm, soft complexion.

Weekly Reset for Soft, Glowing Skin: Use once a week as part of your skincare ritual to deliver an intense hit of hydration and nourishment, helping to soothe the skin and relieve redness due to dryness, while strengthening the skin barrier.
Perfect for Pampering or Gifting: A skin-soothing treat that fits right into your self-care routine—or makes a thoughtful gift for anyone who deserves a relaxing beauty moment.
Vegan, Cruelty-Free & Korean-Made Skincare: Designed in the UK and made in Korea, this mask is 100% vegan and cruelty-free—created with skin, ethics, and planet in mind.
